            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 2,
