      "instruction": "<p>Cover your <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> with<strong> cling film </strong>and bash them with a<strong> rolling pin </strong>until flattened slightly</p><p>Season the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
